panels.content:
OPNFV_Yardstick_NSB_PROX_Baremetal_L2FWD_4Port_Test

The application does Port forwarding without touching packets. It will take packets in from one port and forward them unmodified to another port The KPI is the number of packets per second for a specified packet size with an accepted minimal packet loss
